main event: A man witnessed six-inch-tall humanoid creatures near his car in Lone Prairie, Minnesota on October 12, 1965.
interesting points: The creatures emerged from the side of the road and appeared to be examining a parked automobile,The creatures were described as having no eyes and seemed to scan the area,The sighting was brief as the creatures quickly returned to the side of the road and vanished,The incident was investigated by Jim Townsend, a local radio announcer,The witness felt compelled to document the encounter due to its unusual nature.
witness description: A man driving along a country road
